OL,13, Pioneer were deep into the LaserDisc   
OL,14, market but decided that they needed    
OL,15, a new angle to push into more homes.   
OL,17, They created the LaserActive, a player 
OL,18, that had the capacity to add 'Pacs'.   
OL,20, Four Pacs were released, Megadrive, PC 
OL,21, Engine, Karaoke and PC Connect.        
